{"tid":2315821,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"日本少女漫畫祖師花村榮子病逝 享壽91歲","createTime":"2020-12-07T12:08:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T12:27:06.000Z","uid":4618,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"47b185b5c4b7648ed258f2908cbcfcf66d69761b","tid":2315821,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T12:08:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JGb53bY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJGb53bY.jpg&h=20a2637c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本放送協會（NHK）、日本經濟新聞等媒體報導，少女漫畫開山祖師級的漫畫家花村榮子，3日因多重器官衰竭於東京都內的家中去世，享壽91歲。<br />\n<br />\n花村榮子本名山賀榮子，1959年以創作專門賣給租書店的漫畫「紫之妖精」出道，之後在少女漫畫雜誌「Nakayoshi」、「週刊瑪格麗特」等處發表許多漫畫作品。<br />\n<br />\n其中以1966年的作品「霧中少女」廣受關注，之後並改編成日劇「家庭的秘密」。<br />\n<br />\n花村榮子年逾9旬仍在創作漫畫，曾獲1989年度日本漫畫家協會獎的優秀獎。"},{"pid":"56629828348921ee387bb2dcde717f797108a545","tid":2315821,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T12:13:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1adc2b0c2a884bc76686091a08c61717565c2df","tid":2315821,"uid":356914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T12:13:25.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"5960b9a61594e5bfa4d419d5bd5c2a137f866ac4","tid":2315821,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T12:14:38.000Z","msg":"少女漫畫真係好撚嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a23a51ee486ab2c3895d12f955cd11e5a063c09","tid":2315821,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T12:22:17.000Z","msg":"少女漫已死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7904243ac54e97d97ee778c7af8d1cd5f394a93e","tid":2315821,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T12:27:06.000Z","msg":"Rip"}]}